nce-on-trade-rumours-involving-rohit-sharma-other-mi-players-4707683%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fcsk-ceo-breaks-silence-on-trade-rumours-involving-rohit-sharma-other-mi-players-4707683%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Did%20It%20Too%2C%20Says%20Trinamool%20MP%2C%20Defending%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20Mimicry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20today%20stated%20%26quot%3Bmimicry%20is%20an%20art%26quot%3B%20to%20defend%20his%20parody%20of%20Vice%20President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20outside%20the%20parliament%2C%20and%20said%20he%20has%20high%20respect%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Banerjee%20was%20seen%20mimicking%20Mr%20Dhankhar%2C%20who%20also%20chairs%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20in%20an%20incident%20that%20has%20been%20condemned%20by%20both%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20President.%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20seen%20filming%20the%20act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefending%20his%20act%2C%20he%20said%20he%20had%20not%20intended%20to%20hurt%20anyone%20and%20he%20has%20great%20respect%20for%20Mr%20Dhankhar.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20intention%20to%20hurt%20anyone.%20Mimicry%20is%20an%20art.%20Have%20high%20respect%20for%20me%20(Jagdeep)%20Dhankhar%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Baneree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20a%20%26quot%3Bmock%20parliament%26quot%3B%20was%20going%20on%20when%20his%20act%20was%20recorded%20and%20sought%20to%20know%20if%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20actually%20behaves%20in%20the%20way%20he%20had%20acted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20said%20it%20was%20Lok%20Sabha%20or%20Rajya%20Sabha...a%20mock%20parliament%20was%20going%20on.%20If%20he%20has%20taken%20this%20to%20his%20shoulder%2C%20I%20am%20really%20helpless.%20Does%20he%20really%20behave%20like%20this%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20claimed%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20indulged%20in%20mimicry%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20during%202014-2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20great%20respect%20for%20Dhankhar%20ji.%20But%2C%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20hurt%20anyone...and%20it's%20one%20type%20of%20art.%20Mimicry%20was%20done%20also%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20itself%20during%20the%20last%20term.%20I%20can%20show%20you%20video.%20But%20no%20one%20took%20it%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Mr%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20played%20out%20after%20most%20from%20the%20Opposition%20benches%20were%20suspended%20for%20protesting%20over%20the%20recent%20security%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankhar%20had%20slammed%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20attack%26quot%3B%20and%20in%20a%20symbolic%20gesture%2C%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20MPs%20are%20standing%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20for%20an%20hour%20in%20his%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20even%20PM%20Modi%20had%20dialled%20him%20up%20to%20condemn%20the%20incident%20and%20told%20him%20he%20had%20been%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Breceiving%20end%20of%20such%20insults%26quot%3B%20for%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20this%20remark%2C%20Mr%20Banerjee%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20been%20here%20for%2020%20years.%20How%20can%20he%20link%20it%20with%20any%20past%20incident%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20paid%20a%20visit%20to%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20after%20the%20incident%20and%20termed%20it%20%26quot%3Bdemeaning%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20too%20had%20expressed%20dismay%20over%20the%20incident%20and%20called%20on%20the%20MPs%20to%20ensure%20their%20expression%20is%20within%20the%20norms%20of%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703061000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fjjl8cs48_parliament_625x300_19_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-respect-for-jagdeep-dhankhar-mimicry-an-art-mp-