on%20even%20once%2C%26quot%3B%20Ng%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20it%20chose%20other%20options%20like%20running%20a%20PR%20campaign%20to%20raise%20awareness%20of%20climate%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20some%20might%20argue%20that%20future%20iterations%20of%20AI%20could%20become%20dangerous%2C%20Ng%20felt%20that%20such%20concerns%20weren't%20realistic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BEven%20with%20existing%20technology%2C%20our%20systems%20are%20quite%20safe%2C%20as%20AI%20safety%20research%20progresses%2C%20the%20tech%20will%20become%20even%20safer%2C%26quot%3B%20Ng%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAndrewYNg%2Fstatus%2F1737183906800283980%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20X%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BFears%20of%20advanced%20AI%20being%20'misaligned'%20and%20thereby%20deliberately%20or%20accidentally%20deciding%20to%20wipe%20us%20out%20are%20just%20not%20realistic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BIf%20an%20AI%20is%20smart%20enough%20to%20wipe%20us%20out%2C%20surely%20it's%20also%20smart%20enough%20to%20also%20know%20that's%20not%20what%20it%20should%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENg%20isn't%20the%20only%20tech%20luminary%20to%20have%20weighed%20in%20on%20the%20risks%20and%20dangers%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20April%2C%20Elon%20Musk%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fmedia%2Felon-musk-warns-ais-impact-elections-calls-us-oversight-things-getting-weird-fast%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20thinks%20AI%20poses%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20humanity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp