ygen-feud-that-led-to-temporary-halt-of-apple-watch-models%2Farticleshow%2F106148069.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20is%20in%20a%20legal%20battle%20with%20Masimo%20over%20blood%20oxygen%20monitoring%20technology.%20Masimo%20alleges%20that%20Apple's%20blood%20oxygen%20monitoring%20feature%20infringes%20on%20its%20patented%20technology%20and%20accuses%20Apple%20of%20misappropriating%20trade%20secrets.%20Apple%20denies%20any%20wrongdoing.%20The%20dispute%20is%20being%20played%20out%20in%20courts%20and%20the%20US%20International%20Trade%20Commission%20(USITC)%2C%20with%20a%20final%20verdict%20expected%20before%20Christmas.%20Apple%20has%20halted%20the%20sale%20of%20Apple%20Watch%20Series%209%20and%20Apple%20Watch%20Ultra%202%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20outcome%20could%20have%20implications%20for%20patent%20enforcement%20in%20the%20wearable%20health%20technology%20space.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fexplained-apple-vs-masimo-what-is-the-blood-oxygen-feud-that-led-to-temporary-halt-of-apple-watch-models%2Farticleshow%2F106148069.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDA%20MPs'%20'Stand-Up'%20Gesture%20In%20solidarity%20With%20Vice%20President%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20row%20over%20a%20Trinamool%20MP's%20mimicry%20of%20Vice-President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20belonging%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20today%20staged%20a%20unique%20protest%20to%20show%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Vice-President.%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20said%C2%A0NDA%20members%20would%20stand%20in%20the%20House%20for%20an%20hour%20to%20express%20support%20to%20Mr%20Dhankhar%2C%20Vice-President%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20strongly%20condemn%20this.%20There%20are%20crossing%20all%20limits.%20They%20are%20repeatedly%20insulting%20people%20on%20constitutional%20posts.%20They%20have%20been%20insulting%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%2020%20years%20because%20he%20comes%20from%20a%20humble%20background%20and%20the%20OBC%20community.%20They%20insulted%20the%20President%20because%20she%20is%20a%20tribal%20woman.%20You%20are%20a%20farmer's%20son.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20someone%20from%20the%20Jat%20community%20became%20Vice-President.%20They%20have%20insulted%20this%20post.%20We%20are%20making%20it%20clear%2C%20we%20will%20not%20tolerate%20the%20insult%20of%20the%20Vice-President%20and%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Joshi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20in%20your%20honour%20and%20to%20protest%20against%20them%2C%20we%20will%20stand%20and%20participate%20in%20the%20question%20and%20answer%20session%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20mimicking%20the%20Vice-President%20on%20Parliament%20premises%20has%20raised%20a%20political%20storm.%20Mr%20Banerjee%20is%20among%20the%20141%20Opposition%20MPs%20suspended%20for%20demanding%20a%20statement%20by%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20the%20Parliament%20security%20breach%20last%20week.%20Yesterday%2C%20while%20protesting%20near%20Makar%20Dwar%20to%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building%2C%20the%20Serampore%20MP%20started%20mimicking%20the%20Vice-President.%20Other%20MPs%20were%20seen%20laughing%20as%20Mr%20Banerjee%20imitated%20Mr%20Dhankhar's%20gestures.%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20seen%20filming%20the%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20said%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20that%20he%20had%20seen%20the%20video%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20pained%26quot%3B.%C2%A0Addressing%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20P%20Chidambaram%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BImagine%20what%20I%20felt%20when%20a%20senior%20leader%20of%20your%20party%2C%20an%20MP%2C%20was%20filming%20an%20act%20making%20fun%20of%20m