ed%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20lung%20cancer.%20Known%20for%20her%20role%20as%20Lucy%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Big%20Bang%20Theory%26quot%3B%20shared%20the%20news%20of%20her%20diagnosis%20in%20a%20TikTok%20video.%20Now%2C%20she%20took%20to%20the%20video-sharing%20platform%20and%20posted%20a%20positive%20health%20update%20after%20having%20cancer%20surgery%20last%20week%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%C2%A0Independent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2043-year-old%20said%20that%20she%20is%20cancer-free%20and%20the%20surgery%20to%20treat%20lung%20cancer%20%26quot%3Bwent%20great%26quot%3B.%20She%20said%20in%20the%20video%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20the%20reports%20came%20back%20that%20it%20worked.%20I%20don't%20need%20to%20do%20any%20other%20treatment.%20So%20big%20thank%20you%20to%20all%20my%20doctors%20and%20nurses%20and%20everyone%20that%20took%20just%20really%20great%20care%20of%20me.%20The%20actor%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20thanks%20to%20figuring%20it%20out%20early%20because%20I%20am%20very%2C%20very%20lucky%20and%20I%20know%20that.%26quot%3B%20She%20also%20thanked%20her%20fans%20and%20supporters%20for%20the%20love%2C%20prayers%20and%20kind%20wishes.%20Towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20video%2C%20Ms%20Micucci%20said%20that%20she%20is%20looking%20forward%20to%20Christmas.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20really%20excited%20to%20hand%20out%20with%20my%20little%20boy%20for%20Christmas%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Micucci%20underwent%20the%20surgery%20last%20Friday.%20She%20posted%20a%20video%20at%20that%20time%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%20everybody%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20TikTok%2C%20it's%20a%20'Sick%20Tok.'%20I'm%20in%20the%20hospital%20but%20it's%20because%20I%20had%20lung%20cancer%20surgery%20yesterday.%26quot%3B%20She%20stated%20that%20the%20diagnosis%20was%20a%20surprise%20as%20she%20had%20not%20even%20smoked%20a%20cigarette%20in%20her%20life.%20%26quot%3BThey%20caught%20it%20early.%20It's%20pretty%20weird%20because%20I've%20never%20smoked%2