0response%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20141%20Opposition%20MPs%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20said%20%26quot%3Bdemocracy%20has%20been%20strangulated%20by%20this%20government%26quot%3B%20for%20raising%20a%20%26quot%3Bperfectly%20reasonable%20and%20legitimate%20demand%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDemocracy%20has%20been%20strangulated%20by%20this%20government.%20Never%20before%20have%20so%20many%20Opposition%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20been%20suspended%20from%20the%20house%2C%20and%20that%20too%2C%20simply%20for%20raising%20a%20perfectly%20reasonable%20and%20legitimate%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20said%20at%20the%20Congress%20Parliamentary%20Party%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20Opposition%20MPs%20had%20only%20asked%20for%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20Home%20Minister%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bextraordinary%20events%26quot%3B%20of%20December%2013%2C%20when%20two%20intruders%20trespassed%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20and%20set%20off%20coloured%20smoke%20in%20a%20massive%20security%20breach.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20words%20to%20describe%20the%20arrogance%20with%20which%20this%20request%20was%20treated%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20141%20Opposition%20MPs%20from%20the%20two%20Houses%20have%20been%20suspended%20over%20the%20past%20week%20after%20they%20held%20protests%20demanding%20the%20Home%20Minister's%20statement.%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20has%20maintained%20that%20security%20in%20the%20House%20comes%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20secretariat%20and%20that%20he%20will%20not%20let%20the%20government%20intervene%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20the%20events%20that%20took%20place%20on%20December%2013%20are%20%26quot%3Binexcusable%20and%20cannot%20be%20justified%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20took%20four%20days%20for%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20address%20the%20nation%20and%20express%20his%20views%20on%20the%20incident%2C%20and%20he%20did%20so%20outside%20of%20the%20Parliament.%20By%20so%20doing%2C%20he%20clearly%20indicated%20his%20disdain%20for%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20house%20and%20his%20disregard%20for%20the%20people%20of%20our%20country.%20I%20leave%20it%20to%20you%20to%20imagine%20how%20the%20BJP%20would%20have%20responded%20had%20they%20been%20in%20opposition%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20remarks%20on%20the%20security%20breach%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20told%20Dainik%20Jagran%20newspaper%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%26quot%3B%20incident%20and%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20investigated.%20He%20added%20that%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20need%20for%20a%20debate%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20passage%20of%20key%20legislation%20relating%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20distort%20history%20and%20twist%20historical%20facts%20just%20to%20defame%20great%20patriots%20like%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20have%20been%20running%20a%20relentless%20campaign.%20In%20these%20efforts%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20Home%20Minister%20have%20taken%20the%20lead%20themselves%2C%20but%20we%20will%20not%20be%20intimidated%20or%20cowed%20down.%20We%20will%20persist%20in%20telling%20the%20truth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20position%20on%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20has%20been%20clear%20and%20consistent%3A%20Full%20statehood%20must%20be%20restored%20immediately%2C%20and%20elections%20must%20be%20held%20at%20the%20earliest.%20The%20aspirations%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20are%20equally%20important%2C%20they%20must%20be%20addressed%20and%20shown%20the%20respect%20they%20deserve%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20described%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20with%20a%20rider%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20eyewash%20intended%20to%20mislead%20women%20and%20garner%20their%20votes%20while%20reneging%20on%20that%20which%20is%20rightfully%20owed%20to%20them%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20our%20firm%20belief%20that%20reservation%20for%20women%20must%20be%20implemented%20immediately%20and%20it%20should%20cover%20women%20belonging%20to%20all%20communities%20including%20the%20OBC%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Gandhi%20congratulated%20Congress%20workers%20for%20the%20thumping%20victory%20in%20Telangana%20polls%20and%20said%20the%20party%20must%20strive%20to%20live%20up%20to%20the%20people's%20trust.%20On%20the%20poll%20setbacks%20in%20the%20heartland%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTo%20say%20that%20the%20assembly%20election%20results%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%20have%20been%20very%20disappointing%20for%20our%20party%20is%20an%20understatement.%20The%20Congress%20President%20has%20already%20had%20a%20first%20round%20of%20reviews%20to%20understand%20the%20reasons%20for%20our%20poor%20performance%20and%20draw%20the%20needed%20lessons%20for%20our%20organization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20facing%20enormous%20challenges%2C%20yet%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20our%20fortitude%20and%20resilience%20will%20see%20us%20through.%20Our%20ideology%20and%20our%20values%20are%20our%20guiding%20light%20at%20this%20difficult%20time.%20We%20must%20never%20forget%20that%20our%20leaders%20fought%20against%20insurmountable%20odds%2C%20with%20great%20courage%20and%20fortitude%2C%20to%20give%20us%20our%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20government%2C%20she%20alleged%2C%20has%20conducted%20a%20%26quot%3Bsystematic%20assault%20on%20democracy%20and%20the%20institutions%20that%20are%20its%20essential%20pillars%2C%20including%20Parliament%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDiversity%20has%20been%20the%20strength%20that%20has%20distinguished%20India%20among%20the%20nations%20of%20the%20world.%20We%20have%20always%20been%20proud%20of%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20diverse%20religions%2C%20castes%20and%20ethnicities%20have%20co-existed%20and%20participated%20in%20building%20our%20beautiful%20nation.%20However%2C%20the%20actions%20of%20this%20government%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20methodically%20weakened%20the%20very%20spirit%20of%20this%20unity.%20The%20Constitution%20of%20the%20Republic%20of%20India%20is%20under%20attack.%20Economic%20inequalities%20are%20widening.%20There%20is%20a%20significant%20gap%20between%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20boasts%20about%20economic%20growth%20and%20the%20ground%20reality%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Gandhi%20also%20thanked%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20for%20his%20leadership%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20%26quot%3BMy%20thanks%20also%20go%20out%20to%20our%20CPP%20office%20bearers%20for%20all%20their%20hard%20work%20and%20support.%20I%20am%20also%20grateful%20to%20all%20our%20colleagues%20and%20workers%20for%20campaigning%20tirelessly%20for%20the%20recent%20assembly%20elections.%20We%20must%20channel%20our%20disappointment%20into%20a%20positive%20drive%20for%20the%20coming%20general%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703051460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-03%2F8fbkpfig_sonia-gandhi-_625x300_13_March_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdemocracy-has-been-strangulated-sonia-gandhi-on-suspension-of-141-mps-4707639%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20scathing%20response%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20141%20Opposition%20MPs%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20said%20%26quot%3Bdemocracy%20has%20been%20strangulated%20by%20this%20government%26quot%3B%20for%20raising%20a%20%26quot%3Bperfectly%20reasonable%20and%20legitimate%20demand%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdemocracy-has-been-strangulated-sonia-gandhi-on-suspension-of-141-mps-4707639%22%