out%20a%20Voice%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%3A%20Calculating%20the%20Cost%20of%20Suspending%20MPs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F20111531%2FUntitled-design-5.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20ongoing%20parliament%20session%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2F141-here-are-all-the-mps-suspended-from-parliament-this-winter-session%5C%22%3E141%20MPs%20have%20been%20suspended%20over%20the%20past%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20demanding%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20breach%20of%20security%20at%20parliament%20on%20December%2013.%20The%20unprecedented%20numbers%20have%20left%20lakhs%20of%20electors%20across%20the%20country%20without%20a%20voice%2C%20while%20some%20parties%20have%20been%20shorn%20of%20their%20presence%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20MPs%20are%20suspended%20for%20demanding%20accountability%2C%20a%20little%20more%20of%20democracy%20is%20sucked%20out%20from%20an%20%E2%80%98electoral%20autocracy%E2%80%99%20that%20is%20increasingly%20paying%20attention%20to%20throttling%20independent%20institutions%2C%20whose%20health%20is%20what%20democracies%20rest%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Wire%20calculates%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20suspensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElectors%20denied%20their%20voice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20India%20does%20not%20have%20a%20system%20of%20proportional%20representation%2C%20the%20MPs%20reflect%20the%20voices%20and%20concerns%20of%20their%20electors.%20After%20the%20suspensions%2C14%2C51%2C35%2C108%20electors%20from%2094%20constituencies%20no%20longer%20have%20a%20voice%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F5WLys%2F1%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Electors%20who%20don't%20have%20a%20representative%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22995%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20was%20dire%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20to%20estimate%20the%20number%20of%20electors%20muted%20via%20these%20suspensions%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20divided%20the%20total%20number%20of%20electors%20in%20a%20state%20by%20the%20number%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20that%20state%20has%2C%20as%20a%20broad%20average%20of%20electors%20each%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20represents.%20By%20adding%20these%20numbers%2C%20depending%20upon%20the%20number%20of%20suspensions%20from%20the%20state%2C%20we%20again%20can%20get%20an%20approximation%20of%20the%20number%20of%20voices%20put%20away%20by%20suspending%20their%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20that%20we%20arrive%20at%20through%20this%20calculation%20is%2018%2C43%2C83%2C909%20(18.43%20crore)%20electors%20who%20have%20been%20denied%20a%20voice%20in%20the%20upper%20house%20through%20the%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fjk2Hv%2F1%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Suspended%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20and%20their%20electors%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221246%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EParties%20severely%20depleted%2C%20some%20go%20missing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%20of%20the%20MPs%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20session%20has%20severely%20affected%20the%20presence%20of%20major%20opposition%20parties%20in%20the%20two%20houses%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20strength%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20quarter.%20Other%20parties%20like%20the%20DMK%2C%20TMC%20and%20JDU%20have%20seen%20their%20strength%20deplete%20by%20over%2060%25.%20The%20AAP%20has%20no%20representative%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20anymore%2C%20while%20some%20smaller%20parties%20have%20also%20lost%20their%20representatives%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F61rbE%2F2%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Remaining%20strength%20of%20opposition%20parties%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22613%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20too%2C%20the%20strength%20of%20major%20opposition%20parties%20was%20greatly%20depleted.%20The%20Congress%20was%20down%20to%20a%20fourth%20of%20its%20strength%20as%20was%20the%20TMC%2C%20while%20the%20DMK%20was%20cut%20in%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FILHF0%2F2%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Remaining%20strength%20of%20opposition%20parties%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22483%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIssues%20raised%20by%20MPs%20were%20scotched%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2071%20Questions%20asked%20by%20them%20are%20deleted%20or%20cancelled%2C%20noted%20Maadhyam%2C%20a%20civil%20society%20watchdog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20a%20total%20of%2027%20Questions%20are%20deleted%2C%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%2044%20Questions%20are%20cancelled.%20Govt%20manages%20to%20escape%20answering%20these%20Qs.%20It%20must%20be%20remembered%20that%20MPs%20submitted%20notices%20of%20these%20Qs%20much%20before%20their%20suspension%20(notice%20period%20for%20a%20Q%20is%2015%20days).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20government%20time%20is%20%E2%80%93%20and%20rightly%20so%20%E2%80%93%20spent%20on%20answering%20questions%20raised%20by%20MPs.%20With%20a%20data-deficient%20regime%20in%20place%2C%20where%20there%20is%20also%20a%20good%20deal%20of%20data%20evasion%20and%20manipulation%2C%20parliamentary%20questions%20and%20answers%20are%20often%20a%20key%20data%20resource%20and%20enable%20the%20principle%20of%20accountability%20to%20seep%20into%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaadhyam%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20these%20were%20listed%20for%20answering%20today%2C%20it%20means%20that%20these%20Qs%20successfully%20made%20it%20through%20a%20ballot%20and%20were%20admitted%20for%20answering.%20The%20Ministry%20would%20have%20also%20prepared%20the%20responses%20by%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImportantly%2C%20it%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CMPs%20don%E2%80%99t%20ask%20these%20Qs%20for%20themselves%2C%20they%20ask%20these%20Qs%20for%20us%2C%20on%20our%20behalf.%20The%20information%20given%20in%20response%20to%20these%20Qs%2C%20is%20public%20information%20and%20not%20meant%20for%20private%20consumption%20of%20the%20MP.%20Deleting%20or%20cancelling%20of%20Qs%20also%20deprive%20people%20of%20getting%20this%20information.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%20and%20Amrit%20B.L.S.%20Visualisation%20by%20Amrit%20B.L.S.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703051182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F20111531%2FUntitled-design-5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcost-of-suspending-members-of-parliament%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20some%20parties%20have%20been%20robbed%20of%20a%20presence%20in%20parliament%2C%20it%20is%20the%20people%20who%20suffer.%20The%20Wire%20measures%20just%20how%20much.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcost-of-suspending-members-of-parliament%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SRK%20lights%20up%20Burj%20Khalifa%20with%20Dunki%20trailer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703051095000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106144096%2Cimgsize-72140.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-lights-up-burj-khalifa-with-d