nd%20the%20FIR%20registered%20would%20be%20enough%20to%20raise%20a%20claim.%20The%20oncologist%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20confirm%20whether%20the%20blazer%20was%20under%20insurance.%20The%20hospital%20management%20also%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20whether%20the%20blazer%20was%20hospital%20property%20and%20if%20it%20was%20covered%20under%20insurance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22H%20M%20CHAITHANYA%20SWAMY%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fdoc-gets-stolen-suitcase-back-sans-insured-blazer%2Farticleshow%2F106140637.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DeLorean%20designer%20says%20Tesla's%20Cybertruck%20is%20the%20'Picasso%20of%20automobiles'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla's%20Cybertruck%20(top)%20and%20the%20DeLorean%20DMC-12%20(bottom)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658253dbcefc010bea25588d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla's%20Cybertruck%20(top)%20and%20the%20DeLorean%20DMC-12%20(bottom)%3Cp%3EAndrej%20Sokolow%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20Timothy%20Norris%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGiorgetto%20Giugiaro%20designed%20the%20iconic%20DeLorean%2C%20made%20famous%20by%20the%C2%A0%26quot%3BBack%20to%20the%20Future%26quot%3B%20films.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Italian%20design%20legend%20says%20Tesla's%20Cybertruck%20is%20the%C2%A0%26quot%3Bthe%20Picasso%20of%20automobiles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20DeLorean%20was%20one%20of%20the%20vehicles%20which%20inspired%20the%20Cybertruck's%20design.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EItalian%20design%20legend%20Giorgetto%20Giugiaro%20says%20he%20thinks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla's%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-truck-cybertruck%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECybertruck%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20masterpiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiugiaro%2C%20who%20designed%20the%20cult%20classic%20DeLorean%2C%20called%20the%20Cybertruck%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Picasso%20of%20automobiles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Delorean%20designer%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feurope.autonews.com%2Fcars-concepts%2Fdesigner-giorgetto-giugiaro-thinks-teslas-cybertruck-picasso%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espeaking%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20an%20Italian%20newspaper%20la%20Repubblica%2C%20where%20he%20gushed%20about%20the%20Cybertruck.%20Giugiaro%20said%20he%20expects%20the%20vehicle%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bhugely%20successful%20because%20people%20want%20to%20stand%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20Cybertruck%20is%20notable%20for%20being%20the%20first%20stainless%20steel%20vehicle%20to%20be%20produced%20since%20Giugiaro's%20DeLorean.%20The%20DeLorean%2C%20which%20appeared%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BBack%20to%20the%20Future%26quot%3B%20film%20series%2C%20was%20launched%20in%20the%2080s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20does%20not%20represent%20the%20search%20for%20harmony%20and%20perfection%20but%20for%20emotion%20and%20robustness%2C%26quot%3B%20Giugiaro%20said%20of%20the%20Cybertruck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20first%20time%20Giugiaro%20has%20heaped%20praise%20on%20the%20Cybertruck.%20He%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2023%2F11%2F14%2F1212575764%2Ftesla-cybertruck-design-delorean-designer-giorgetto-giugiaro-interview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENPR%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20interview%20last%20month%20that%20the%20truck%20would%20be%20a%20hit%20with%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20wants%20to%20distinguish%20themselves.%20It's%20a%20market%20necessity%2C%20and%20the%20Cybertruck%20will%20surely%20be%20successful%2C%20I'm%20sure%20of%20it.%20I'm%20convinced%20it%20will%20find%20its%20admirers%2C%26quot%3B%20Giugiaro%20said%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vote%20of%20confidence%20from%20Giugiaro%20would%20probably%20make%20Tesla%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20very%20happy.%20Giugiaro's%20DeLorean%20was%20one%20of%20the%20vehicles%20that%20inspired%20the%20Cybertruck's%20design%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearly-tesla-cybertruck-design-ideas-inspiration-curves-elon-musk-photo-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWalter%20Isaacson's%20biography%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20also%20has%20big%20plans%20for%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%20if%20his%20latest%20posts%20on%20X%20are%20any%20indication.%20On%20Monday%2C%20Musk%20said%20Tesla%20would%20be%20rolling%20out%20a%20%26quot%3Bmod%20package%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20allow%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-says-you-can-use-cybertruck-as-a-boat-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECybertruck%20to%20function%20as%20a%20boat%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20going%20to%20offer%20a%20mod%20package%20that%20enables%20Cybertruck%20to%20traverse%20at%20least%20100m%20of%20water%20as%20a%20boat%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1736943517115482218%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BMostly%20just%20need%20to%20upgrade%20cabin%20door%20seals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Tesla%20and%20Giugiaro%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelorean-designer-calls-cybertruck-the-picasso-of-automobiles-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703042861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658253dbcefc010bea25588d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelorean-designer-calls-cybertruck-the-picasso-of-automobiles-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Giorgetto%20Giugiaro%20says%20he%20expects%20the%20vehicle%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bhugely%20successful%20because%20people%20want%20to%20stand%20out.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A186%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelorean-designer-calls-cybertruck-the-picasso-of-automobiles-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MP%3A%20With%20a%20Change%20of%20Guard%2C%20Can%20the%20Congress%20Mount%20a%20Challenge%20Against%20the%20BJP%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19212110%2FEffect-35.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhopal%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20unceremonious%20ouster%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%20as%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20president%20last%20Saturday%20has%20considerably%20lessened%20the%20sense%20of%20despondency%20among%20party%20workers%20in%20the%20state%20over%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20stunning%20defeat%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeldom%2C%20if%20ever%2C%20has%20the%20state%20Congress%20seen%20so%20much%20unconcealed%20glee%20on%20the%20faces%20of%20so%20many%20of%20its%20cadres%20before%20the%20departure%20of%20its%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20only%20Rahul%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20taken%20this%20step%20before%20the%20assembly%20elections!%E2%80%9D%20was%20the%20overwhelming%20reaction%20in%20the%20Congress.%20Another%20common%20reaction%20was%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EDer%20aaye%2C%20durust%20aaye%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Better%20late%20than%20never).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20see%20the%20decision%20as%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise%2C%20arguing%20that%20but%20for%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20in%20the%20election%2C%20the%20high%20command%20might%20not%20have%20deemed%20it%20proper%20to%20rid%20the%20state%20Congress%20of%20the%20two-man%20gerontocracy%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%20(77)%20and%20Digvijay%20Singh%20(76)%20given%20their%20proximity%20to%20the%20Gandhi%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20held%20sway%20over%20the%20Congress%20for%20more%20than%20four%20decades.%20Although%20Digvijay%20Singh%20did%20not%20hold%20any%20post%20in%20the%20state%20Congress%20after%20he%20became%20chief%20minister%20in%201993%2C%20he%20continued%20to%20use%20his%20enormous%20clout%20to%20meddle%20in%20party%20affairs%20and%20influence%20his%20successor%20Pradesh%20Congress%20committee%20(PCC)%20presidents%20all%20these%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20state%20politics%20as%20PCC%20chief%20in%202017%20and%20subsequent%20stint%20in%20the%20short-lived%20Congress%20government%20as%20chief%20minister%20facilitated%20Digvijay%20Singh%20to%20acquire%20more%20power%20in%20the%20party.%20Both%20the%20veterans%20tightly%20controlled%20the%20party%20for%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20it%20not%20been%20for%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20crushing%20defeat%2C%20the%20Kamal%20Nath-Digvijay%20Singh%20pair%20would%20have%20held%20on%20to%20their%20commanding%20position.%20The%20defeat%20sealed%20their%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbehind-congress-defeat-madhya-pradesh-kamal-nath-rejection%5C%22%3EBehind%20Congress%20Defeat%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20Clear%20Rejection%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20Leadership%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClear%20marching%20order%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20election%20results%20were%20out%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20summoned%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20Digvijay%20Singh%20and%20other%20state%20leaders%20to%20New%20Delhi%20to%20express%20his%20utter%20disappointment%20over%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20show%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%2C%20Kharge%20told%20Kamal%20Nath%20point%20blank%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20Congress%20workers%20wanted%20him%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESensing%20that%20his%20position%20is%20utterly%20untenable%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20pushed%20the%20name%20of%20his%20loyalist%20MLA%20Bala%20Bachchan%20for%20the%20post%20of%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%2C%20while%20seeking%20to%20continue%20as%20PCC%20chief%20till%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigvijay%20Singh%20pushed%20the%20name%20of%20Omkar%20Singh%20Marker%20and%20Ajay%20Singh%20for%20the%20leader%20of%20opposition%20post%20and%20supported%20Kamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20request%20for%20continuation.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20summarily%20rejected%20their%20pleas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17192201%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje-1024x683.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17192201%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17192201%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17192201%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680509%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKamal%20Nath%2C%20Digvijay%20Singh%20and%20others%20release%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20on%20October%2017.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40OfficeofKNath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20go%2C%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20nominated%20its%20picks%20for%20three%20important%20posts.%20Jitu%20Patwari%20(OBC)%20will%20be%20state%20Congress%20president%2C%20Umang%20Singhar%20(tribal)%20will%20be%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20and%20Hemant%20Katare%20(Brahmin)%20to%20be%20the%20deputy%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDirect%20association%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20leaders%2C%20aged%20below%2050%2C%20are%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20loyalists%20and%20owe%20no%20allegiance%20to%20any%20stalwarts%20in%20the%20state%20Congress.%20Both%20Patwari%20(50)%20and%20Singhar%20(49)%20have%20experience%20working%20under%20the%20direct%20mentorship%20of%20the%20former%20AICC%20president.%20Jitu%20Patwari%20was%20co-convener%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20in%20its%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20phase.%20He%20also%20shot%20into%20the%20limelight%20in%202017%20when%20the%20young%20Congress%20leader%20drove%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20his%20motorbike%20in%20Mandsaur.%20Gandhi%20had%20gone%20there%20to%20meet%20the%20families%20of%20the%20farmers%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20police%20firing%20in%20June%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Patwari%20has%20continued%20to%20thrive%20in%20state%20politics%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20link%20with%20the%20MP%20from%20Wayanad.%20In%20the%20Kamal%20Nath%20government%2C%20Patwari%20was%20a%20cabinet%20minister.%20After%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20government%2C%20the%20rising%20Congress%20star%20was%20made%20media%20chief%20in%20the%20state%20Congress.%20In%20the%20recently%20held%20election%2C%20the%20new%20PCC%20chief%20was%20co-chairman%20of%20the%20campaign%20committee.%20He%20had%20also%20been%20one%20of%20the%20four%20working%20presidents%20of%20the%20MPCC%20under%20Kamal%20Nath.%20Besides%2C%20he%20is%20on%20the%20panel%20of%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20national%20spokespersons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUmang%20Singhar%20has%20a%20long%20and%20direct%20association%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20Both%20undertook%20a%20nationwide%20tour%20of%20tribal%20areas%20together.%20Singhar%20was%20picked%20up%20to%20help%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20in%20Amethi%20in%20the%202009%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Again%2C%20it%20was%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20who%20recommended%20Umang%E2%80%99s%20candidacy%20for%20the%20Gandhwani%20seat%20in%20the%20Dhar%20district%20for%20assembly%20election%20in%202008.%20Since%20then%20Umang%20won%20the%20successive%20assembly%20polls%20on%20this%20seat%20with%20huge%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurtain%20on%20Kamal%20Nath-Digvijay%20era%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20men%20and%20women%20seem%20to%20be%20happier%20over%20the%20choice%20of%20his%20successor%2C%20Jitu%20Patwari%2C%20than%20the%20exit%20of%20septuagenarian%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20who%20is%20being%20held%20squarely%20responsible%20for%20squandering%20away%20a%20golden%20opportunity%20to%20avenge%20the%20fall%20of%20his%20government%20three%20years%20ago.%20His%20exit%20rings%20the%20curtain%20down%20on%20the%20era%20of%20the%20vintage-80s%20leadership.%20More%20importantly%2C%20it%20heralds%20an%20era%20of%20youth%20leadership%20that%20has%20earned%20its%20stripe%20without%20the%20clutches%20of%20dynastic%2C%20feudalistic%2C%20or%20money%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20new%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20LoP%20Singhar%20is%20the%20nephew%20of%20fiery%20tribal%20leader%20late%20Jamuna%20Devi%20who%20had%20also%20been%20in%20this%20post%20in%20the%20BJP%20government.%20However%2C%20Singhar%20did%20not%20bask%20in%20the%20reflected%20glory%20of%20his%20more%20illustrious%20aunty.%20He%20carved%20his%20niche%20in%20the%20party%20by%20the%20sheer%20dint%20of%20hard%20work%20as%20a%20Youth%20Congress%20leader%20in%20the%20predominantly%20tribal%20district%20that%20endeared%20him%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20cabinet%20minister%2C%20Singhar%20is%20the%20most%20prominent%20tribal%20leader%20in%20the%20Congress.%20Having%20worked%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20tribal%20issues%20nationally%2C%20he%20is%20expected%20to%20raise%20the%20problems%20of%20the%2021%25%20Adivasi%20population%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20with%20greater%20force%20than%20any%20of%20his%20predecessors%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20deputy%20Hemand%20Katare%20is%20the%20son%20of%20former%20minister%20and%20former%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20late%20Satyadeo%20Katare.%20Katare%20junior%20won%20on%20the%20Ater%20seat%20in%202017%20by%20election%20caused%20due%20to%20death%20of%20his%20father.%20He%20lost%20the%202018%20election%20but%20won%20again%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETeam%20Rahul%20in%20the%20making%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20elevating%20Patwari%20and%20Singhar%20as%20state%20chief%20and%20LoP%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20appointed%20two%20more%20young%20leaders%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20national%20bodies%20of%20the%20Congress%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20Kamleshwar%20Patel%20(OBC)%2C%20who%20lost%20this%20election%2C%20was%20nominated%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%2C%20and%20Omkar%20Singh%20Markam%20(tribal)%2C%20who%20won%20the%20election%20from%20Dindori%2C%20was%20inducted%20into%20the%2012-member%20Congress%20Parliamentary%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20command%20of%20the%20MP%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20youth%20brigade%20is%20completely%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Jitu%20Patwari%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrandson%20of%20a%20freedom%20fighter%2C%20the%20newly%20appointed%20state%20Congress%20president%20Jitu%20Patwari%20has%20risen%20in%20politics%20from%20being%20a%20Panchyat%20member%20in%20his%20native%20village%20in%20the%20Indore%20district.%20Belonging%20to%20the%20Khati%20community%20(Other%20Backward%20Caste)%2C%20Jitu%20Patwari%20has%20come%20up%20the%20organisational%20ladder%20step%20by%20step.%20From%20Panchayat%2C%20he%20was%20active%20in%20the%20Youth%20Congress%20and%20rose%20to%20become%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20state%20president.%20A%20law%20graduate%20from%20Devi%20Ahilya%20University%2C%20Indore%2C%20Jitu%20Patwari%20became%20an%20MLA%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202013.%20He%20retained%20the%20Rau%20seat%20in%202018%20but%20lost%20in%20the%202023%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20his%20appointment%2C%20Patwari%20thanked%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20for%20giving%20a%20big%20responsibility%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Csmall%20worker%E2%80%9D%20like%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20faced%20defeat%20in%20the%20recent%20assembly%20elections%20and%20I%20am%20aware%20that%20the%20Congress%20faces%20the%20challenge%20of%20putting%20up%20a%20good%20performance%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20We%20will%20face%20this%20challenge%20based%20on%20collective%20leadership%20and%20deliver%20positive%20results%20while%20taking%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20ideology%20from%20door-to-door%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFear%20of%20false%20dawn%20remains%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20even%20as%20the%20state%20Congress%20is%20gung-ho%20about%20the%20dawn%20of%20a%20new%20era%20of%20youth%20leadership%2C%20the%20apprehension%20of%20this%20being%20a%20false%20dawn%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out.%20The%20Congress%20may%20have%20injected%20youthfulness%20in%20the%20leadership%2C%20and%20the%20party%20may%20also%20celebrate%20getting%20the%20right%20caste%20combination%20(OBC%2C%20tribal%20and%20Brahmin)%2C%20but%20it%20remains%20a%20herculean%20task%20ahead%20for%20the%20young%20trio%20to%20revive%20the%20disheartened%20cadres%20at%20the%20grassroots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenge%20before%20the%20trio%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20toughest%20challenge%20for%20the%20new%20leadership%20is%20to%20mount%20a%20narrative%20in%20the%20Congress%20which%20runs%20ideologically%20counter%20to%20that%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamal%20Nath%20miserably%20failed%20to%20do%20so.%20He%20rather%20peremptorily%20presumed%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20can%20be%20neutralised%20by%20covering%20the%20Congress%20with%20a%20similar%20saffron%20sheet.%20He%20unabashedly%20mimicked%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20tactics%20of%20wooing%20devout%20Hindus%20and%20ended%20up%20amplifying%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20agenda.%20As%20the%20election%20results%20show%2C%20the%20voters%20opted%20for%20the%20original%20proponent%20of%20Hindutva%20that%20is%20the%20BJP%20than%20the%20Johnny-come-lately%20imitator%20that%20the%20Congress%20tried%20to%20become.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELegacy%20of%20timid%20Congress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20to%20be%20fair%20to%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20he%20had%20inherited%20the%2015-year-old%20legacy%20of%20a%20timid%20and%20dispirited%20Congress%20when%20he%20took%20over%20as%20its%20chief%20in%20April%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20long%20rule%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20through%20its%20persistent%20propaganda%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20had%20managed%20to%20instil%20the%20fear%20in%20the%20Congress%20that%20any%20talk%20of%20secularism%20would%20make%20it%20look%20anti-Hindu.%20The%20fear%20pervaded%20down%20to%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20whenever%20Digvijay%20Singh%20tweeted%20his%20views%20on%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20communal%20politics%20against%20Muslims%2C%20his%20own%20party%20workers%20would%20privately%20blame%20the%20veteran%20leader%20for%20damaging%20the%20Congress%20rather%20than%20standing%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Congress%20ecosystem%2C%20the%20fear%20of%20being%20branded%20pro-Muslim%20seeped%20so%20deep%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20secularist%20moorings%20got%20lost%20in%20the%20ideological%20confusion.%20Sensing%20objection%20to%20his%20avowedly%20secularist%20views%2C%20Digvijay%20Singh%20too%2C%20of%20late%2C%20became%20rather%20cagey%20in%20bashing%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIdeological%20drift%20went%20on%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20PCC%20chief%20before%20Kamal%20Nath%20addressed%20this%20ideological%20drift%20in%20the%20Congress%20effectively%2C%20be%20they%20Subhash%20Yadav%2C%20Suresh%20Pachouri%20and%20Arun%20Yadav.%20None%20of%20them%20summoned%20enough%20courage%20to%20present%20the%20Congress%20as%20a%20strong%20secularist%20alternative%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Instead%2C%20they%20succumbed%20to%20the%20lure%20of%20saffron%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Kamal%20Nath%20took%20over%20as%20MPCC%20chief%20one%20and%20half%20years%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%202018%2C%20his%20sole%20objective%20was%20to%20become%20the%20next%20chief%20minister.%20An%20ideology-neutral%20industrialist%20that%20he%20is%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%20introduced%20corporate%20style%20of%20functioning%20in%20the%20Congress.%20He%20succeeded%20to%20some%20extent.%20The%20Congress%20organisation%20sprung%20into%20life%2C%20its%20head%20office%20became%20swankier%2C%20other%20offices%20too%20buzzed%20with%20activity%2C%20but%20the%20cadres%20remained%20unenthusiastic%20about%20fighting%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20ideological%20plane.%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20on%20his%20part%2C%20was%20focused%20on%20a%20corporate-style%20fight%20against%20the%20BJP.%20He%20had%20no%20interest%20whatsoever%20in%20priming%20the%20Congress%20cadres%20for%20a%20durable%20ideological%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fortuitous%20victory%20of%20the%20Congress%20(it%20fell%20two%20seats%20short%20of%20the%20majority%20)%20in%20the%202018%20assembly%20election%20further%20convinced%20the%20PCC%20president%20that%20the%20BJP%20can%20be%20defeated%20in%20a%20corporate%20style%20such%20as%20by%20conducting%20surveys%20through%20deploying%20modern%20gadgets.%20He%20acted%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20company%20and%20treated%20other%20leaders%20like%20subordinates%20who%20must%20obey%20his%20orders%20without%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20his%20successor%20Jitu%20Patwari%20is%20a%20quintessential%20down-to-earth%20leader.%20His%20political%20journey%20so%20far%20is%20testimony%20to%20his%20ability%20to%20easily%20connect%20with%20grassroots%20workers.%20His%20belonging%20to%20the%20OBC%20community%20could%20be%20an%20asset%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20provided%20he%20can%20win%20over%2050%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%20to%20the%20Congress%20side%20on%20the%20debate%20about%20a%20caste-based%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20issue%20of%20secularism%2C%20Patwari%20has%20been%20quite%20articulate%20in%20TV%20debates.%20However%2C%20mouthing%20platitudes%20on%20ideology%20in%20TV%20debates%20is%20one%20thing%2C%20and%20inspiring%20the%20Congress%20workers%20to%20shed%20the%20fear%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20is%20quite%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703042532000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19212110%2FEffect-35.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmp-with-a-change-of-guard-can-the-congress-mount-a-challenge-against-the-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Following%20the%20drubbing%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20party%20leadership%20was%20quick%20to%20show%20the%20door%20to%20Kamal%20Nath.%20While%20Jitu%20Patwari%20(OBC)%20has%20been%20made%20the%20party%20chief%2C%20Umang%20Singhar%20(tribal)%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmp-with-a-change-of-guard-can-the-congress-mount-a-challenge-against-the-bj