study%2C%20told%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20about%202%25%20of%20the%20%24750%20per%20month%20was%20spent%20on%20alcohol%2C%20cigarettes%2C%20or%20drugs%2C%20Henwood%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20Times%3B%20the%20majority%20of%20that%20money%20was%20spent%20on%20cigarettes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHenwood%2C%20the%20director%20for%20the%20Center%20for%20Homelessness%2C%20Housing%20and%20Health%20Equity%20Research%20at%20the%20USC%20Suzanne%20Dworak-Peck%20School%20of%20Social%20Work%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurekalert.org%2Fnews-releases%2F1011316%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20different%20needs%2C%20and%20we're%20empowering%20them%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20is%20going%20to%20help%20them%20individually.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20recipient%20of%20the%20money%20told%20the%20researchers%20that%20they%20used%20the%20cash%20to%20%26quot%3Bcatch%20up%20on%20bills%26quot%3B%20and%20for%20a%20much-needed%20car%20repair%2C%20while%20another%20reported%20that%20they%20spent%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20the%20money%20on%20food%20on%20the%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20received%20the%20funds%2C%20the%20proportion%20of%20people%20who%20reported%20being%20unsheltered%20in%20the%20past%20month%20dropped%20from%2030%25%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20trial%20to%20under%2012%25%20at%20the%20six-month%20follow-up%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20in%20the%20control%20group%20had%20a%20small%20decrease%20from%2028%25%20to%2023%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20behind%20the%20study%20plan%20to%20publish%20a%20follow-up%20report%20based%20on%20the%20full%20year%20of%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOther%20basic%20income%20experiments%20showed%20similar%20positive%20results%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20out%20of%20Los%20Angeles%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20basic%20income%20experiments%20that%20appear%20to%