0top%20Russia%20watcher%20Mark%20Galeotti%2C%20writing%20for%20the%20Global%20Initiative%20against%20Transnational%20Organized%20Crime%2C%C2%A0reported%20that%20Russia's%20invasion%20has%20resulted%20in%20the%20overhaul%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eof%20major%20narcotics%20routes%20once%20used%20by%20Russian%20gangs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20war%2C%20Russia%20served%20as%20a%20hub%20for%20cross-border%20flows%20of%20all%20types%20of%20illicit%20products%2C%20such%20as%20money%2C%20guns%2C%20drugs%2C%20and%20people%20throughout%20Europe%20and%20beyond.%20Ukraine's%20criminal%20underworld%20once%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20distribution%2C%20Galeotti%20said%20during%20a%20Monday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobalinitiative.net%2Fanalysis%2Fthe-russian-underworld-since-the-ukraine-invasion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresentation%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20since%20Russia%20invaded%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022%2C%20Ukrainian%20gangsters%20have%20suddenly%20%26quot%3Brediscovered%20their%20patriotism%2C%26quot%3B%20Galeotti%20said%20during%20the%20presentation%2C%20and%20are%20refusing%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20Russians.%20Ukraine's%20cold%20shoulder%20coupled%20with%20the%20closing%20of%20land%20routes%20in%20countries%20like%20Finland%20have%20forced%20Russian%20gangsters%20to%20find%20alternative%20drug%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20get%20product%20out%20of%20Russia%20and%20into%20other%20parts%20of%20Europe%2C%20traffickers%20are%20increasingly%20turning%20to%20Belarus%20as%20a%20new%20crucial%20transit%20hub%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20border%20controls%20set%20up%20throughout%20Europe%2C%20heroin%2C%20cocaine%2C%20and%20other%20narcotics%20are%20being%20smuggled%20out%20of%20Russia%20via%20Belarus%2C%20Galeotti%20said%2C%20while%20sanctioned%20items%20such%20as%20microchips%20and%20luxury%20goods%20are%20being%20smuggled%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lar