0typically%20do.%20This%20includes%20cycling%2C%20boxing%2C%20resistance%20training%2C%20strength%20training%2C%20running%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20Though%20it's%20hard%20to%20pinpoint%20its%20exact%20impact%20on%20my%20training%2C%20one%20thing%20I%20did%20notice%20was%20how%20much%20lighter%20I%20felt%20on%20runs%20when%20I%20wasn't%20wearing%20it.%20I%20logged%20faster%20mile%20times%20and%20was%20able%20to%20run%20longer%20and%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20don't%20wear%20the%20apparel%20for%20every%20workout%20now%20as%20I%20did%20when%20I%20was%20exhaustively%20testing%20it%2C%20I%C2%A0do%20make%20sure%20it's%20in%20my%20wardrobe%20at%20least%20three%20times%20a%20week%20(and%20I%20switch%20up%20what%20kinds%20of%20workouts%20I%20use%20it%20for%20often).%20It's%20a%20unique%20take%20on%20adding%20resistance%20to%20your%20workouts%2C%20and%20one%20that's%20a%20bit%20more%20versatile%20than%20throwing%20on%20a%20weighted%20vest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20multi-sport%20training%3A%20NoBull%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221138%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Person%20holding%20a%20kettlebell%20-%20best%20workout%20clothes%20for%20men%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F618acc7e23745d001825ba78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENoBull%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EVersatile%20clothing%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20workout%20types%2C%20a%20huge%20range%20of%20sizes%20and%20styles%20for%20all%20body%20types%2C%20also%20offers%20accessories%20like%20gym%20bags%2C%20cross-training%20shoes%2C%20headbands%2C%20and%20towels%2C%20moderate%20prices%2C%20durable%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ESizing%20can%20run%20small%20in%20some%20pieces%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20the%20kind%20of%20person%20who%20likes%20to%20keep%20active%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20ways%2C%20be%20it%20running%2C%20cycling%2C%20lifting%20weights%2C%20or%20even%20doing%20CrossFit%2C%20then%20the%20workout%20apparel%20from%20NoBull%20is%20one%20to%20pay%20attention%20to.%20From%20its%20shorts%20and%20workout%20tops%20to%20its%20shoes%2C%20gym%20bags%2C%20and%20casual%20wear%2C%20NoBull%20has%20something%20for%20everyone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20keeps%20active%20every%20day%2C%20and%20who%20tries%20to%20do%20something%20different%20as%20often%20as%20possible%2C%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20try%20the%20gear%20from%20NoBull.%20I'd%20seen%20ads%20on%20Instagram%20for%20the%20brand%20for%20some%20time%20but%20had%20chalked%20it%20up%20to%20just%20that%3A%20a%20social%20media-promoted%20athletic%20brand%20that%20was%20just%20like%20any%20of%20the%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20oh%20was%20I%20wrong.%20The%20gear%20I%20received%20from%20NoBull%20to%20test%20quickly%20changed%20my%20perspective.%20Not%20only%20did%20I%20find%20the%20apparel%20to%20be%20among%20the%20most%20comfortable%20in%20terms%20of%20fit%2C%20but%20the%20styles%20were%20all%20versatile%20enough%20that%20it%20didn't%20matter%20if%20I%20was%20running%2C%20doing%20a%20resistance%20band%20workout%2C%20or%20boxing.%20That%20is%20to%20say%20that%20aside%20from%20just%20being%20comfortable%2C%20they%20also%20wick%20sweat%20incredibly%20well%20and%20are%20stretchy%20enough%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20movements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20tried%20out%20a%20pair%20of%20NoBull's%20running%20shoes%20which%20aside%20from%20using%20them%20to%20work%20out%2C%20became%20one%20of%20my%20go-to%20travel%20shoes%20(they're%20%3Cem%3Eincredibly%3C%2Fem%3E%20comfortable%20if%20that%20wasn't%20already%20clear).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20tiny%20nitpick%20to%20point%20out%20is%20the%20sizing%20can%20be%20a%20little%20small%2C%20so%20if%20you're%20in%20between%20sizes%2C%20go%20for%20the%20next%20one%20up%20just%20to%20be%20safe.%20The%20site%20does%20have%20a%20size%20guide%20for%20each%20piece%2C%20so%20I%20recommend%20referencing%20that%20before%20buying%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20I%20test%20workout%20clothes%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20the%20pieces%20of%20workout%20clothing%20highlighted%20in%20this%20guide%20went%20through%20a%20series%20of%20tests%20to%20see%20how%20well%20it%20performed%20across%20these%20four%20categories%3A%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EFit%2C%20function%2C%20durability%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Evalue%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Here's%20how%20each%20category%20specifically%20factored%20into%20which%20athletic%20wear%20ultimately%20made%20this%20guide%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EFit.%20Comfort.%20This%20category%20could've%20been%20called%20either%20but%20we%20went%20with%20%26quot%3Bfit%26quot%3B%20specifically%20because%20a%20well-fitting%20piece%20of%20workout%20clothing%20will%20almost%20always%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20be%20comfortable.%20Fit%20is%20also%20more%20than%20just%20making%20sure%20you%20select%20the%20right%20size%20but%20is%20also%20about%20how%20it%20feels%20while%20working%20out.%20The%20rise%20of%20stretch%20fabrics%20has%20helped%20this%20category%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFunction%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20basic%20function%20of%20workout%20clothing%20should%20be%20to%20keep%20you%20comfortable%2C%20move%20along%20with%20how%20you%20work%20out%2C%20and%20maybe%20even%20wick%20some%20sweat.%20Thankfully%2C%20today's%20selection%20of%20workout%20gear%20does%20it%20all.%20When%20testing%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20how%20well%20a%20brand's%20sweat-wicking%20tech%20worked%2C%20whether%20it%20repelled%20odors%2C%20and%20if%20the%20four-way%20stretch%20fabric%20was%20able%20to%20stretch%20in%20all%20directions.%20Other%20functions%20I%20assessed%20were%20the%20comfort%20of%20built-in%20short%20liners%20and%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20other%20materials%20(like%20Merino).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EPremium%20workout%20clothing%20(i.e.%20the%20gear%20that's%20worth%20your%20money)%20should%20last%20longer%20than%20a%20few%20months%20of%20heavy%20use%20and%20heavy%20cleaning.%20This%20means%20it%20should%20keep%20its%20fit%20and%20still%20offer%20whatever%20suite%20of%20extra%20features%20long%20after%20you%20purchase%20it%20and%20wear%20it%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20This%20category%20is%20best%20served%20as%20a%20long-term%20assessment%2C%20and%20we've%20included%20updated%20insight%20on%20some%20pieces%20where%20we're%20able.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EValue%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAs%20mentioned%20above%2C%20the%20best%20workout%20gear%20won't%20always%20be%20entirely%20cheap.%20Though%20we've%20included%20a%20budget%20brand%20in%20this%20guide%20(and%20one%20we%20stand%20behind)%2C%20it's%20oftentimes%20worth%20it%20to%20spend%20a%20little%20more%20on%20workout%20clothing%20that's%20designed%20to%20last%20(as%20opposed%20to%20spending%20less%20on%20something%20you'll%20have%20to%20replace%20over%20and%20over%20again).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQs%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20should%20I%20consider%20when%20shopping%20for%20workout%20clothes%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20first%20want%20to%20think%20about%20the%20type%20of%20exercise%20you%20do%20most%20often.%20Clothing%20is%20just%20another%20tool%20to%20help%20or%20hinder%20you%2C%20so%20be%20sure%20you're%20buying%20the%20right%20gear%20for%20the%20right%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20piece%20of%20clothing's%20ability%20to%20withstand%20cycles%20in%20the%20washing%20machine%20is%20also%20a%20key%20quality.%20You'll%20likely%20be%20sweating%20through%20these%20clothes%20a%20lot%20and%20(hopefully)%20putting%20them%20in%20the%20laundry%20quite%20often.%20If%20you're%20buying%20flimsily%20made%20clothing%2C%20you'll%20have%20to%20replace%20them%20much%20more%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsider%20how%20multi-purpose%20you%20need%20your%20gear%20to%20be%2C%20too.%20Are%20you%20only%20going%20to%20wear%20those%20joggers%20to%20the%20gym%2C%20or%20are%20they%20also%20for%20lounging%20around%3F%20Is%20that%20long-sleeved%20tee%20just%20as%20good%20for%20your%20run%20as%20it%20is%20for%20running%20errands%20on%20the%20weekend%3F%20The%20workout%20clothing%20you%20wear%20doesn't%20%3Cem%3Ehave%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20cover%20a%20range%20of%20use%20cases%20but%20some%20are%20designed%20for%20more%20than%20just%20running%20or%20lifting%20weights%20(and%20can%20make%20your%20investment%20stretch%20a%20little%20further).%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20differences%20between%20men's%20and%20women's%20workout%20clothes%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBrands%20differentiate%20men's%20and%20women's%20workout%20clothing%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20specific%20design%20choices%2C%20as%20well%20as%20colorways%20and%20style.%20Men's%20workout%20shirts%20tend%20to%20be%20cut%20to%20fit%20broader%20shoulders%20while%20men's%20shorts%20offer%20more%20leg%20coverage%20(though%20this%20isn't%20always%20the%20case)%20and%20added%20space%20in%20the%20crotch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen's%20workout%20shirts%20are%20often%20narrower%20and%20form-fitting%2C%20have%20shorter%20sleeves%2C%20and%20are%20sometimes%20designed%20to%20fit%20tighter%20around%20the%20arms.%20Shorts%20designed%20for%20women%20tend%20to%20feature%20a%20cut%20that%20accommodates%20rounder%20hips%2C%20are%20void%20of%20any%20added%20space%20in%20the%20crotch%2C%20and%20may%20also%20have%20a%20wider%20waistband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20differences%2C%20finding%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%26quot%3B%20workout%20clothing%20comes%20down%20to%20what%20fits%20you%20best%20and%20what%20feels%20comfortable%20while%20you%20work%20out.%20Although%20this%20piece%20focuses%20specifically%20on%20workout%20clothing%20designed%20for%20cisgender%20men%2C%20we%20also%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fbest-workout-clothes-women%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanot