lick%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20its%20employees%20now%20faced%20an%20uncertain%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CComing%20at%20the%20year-end%20festive%20season%2C%20this%20sudden%20action%20has%20left%20all%20our%20employees%20shocked.%20Since%20there%20is%20no%20indication%20of%20when%20our%20accounts%20will%20become%20accessible%2C%20there%20is%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20all%20employees%20and%20their%20families%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20are%20completely%20dependent%20on%20salaries%20from%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20statement%20added%20that%20it%20had%20not%20violated%20any%20laws%2C%20including%20tax%20regulations.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20claims%20levelled%20by%20the%20income%20tax%20department%20are%20without%20any%20basis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLegal%20appeals%20against%20this%20unjust%20and%20cruel%20measure%20will%20be%20initiated%20at%20the%20earliest%E2%80%9D%20following%20a%20review%20of%20Monday%E2%80%99s%20developments%2C%20the%20statement%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20portal%E2%80%99s%20founder%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20its%20HR%20dead%20Amit%20Chakraborty%20are%20in%20jail%20since%20October%203%20after%20being%20arrested%20by%20the%20Delhi%20police%20%E2%80%93%20an%20arm%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20%E2%80%93%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%20a%20draconian%20anti-terror%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20police%E2%80%99s%20special%20cell%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1057022%2Fno-one-spared-in-newsclick-raids-young-staffers-part-time-employees-freelance-contributors%5C%22%3Econfiscated%20the%20devices%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20staff%20and%20contributors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdelhi-police-terror-fir-against-newsclick-names-chinese-firms-xiaomi-vivo-puts-lawyers-in-crosshairs%5C%22%3EFIR%20against%20Purkayastha%20and%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20alleges%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20that%20the%20portal%C2%A0used%20a%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20amount%E2%80%9D%20of%20Chinese%20funding%20to%20publish%20%E2%80%9Cpaid%20news%E2%80%9D%20criticising%20Indian%20government%20policies%20and%20promoting%20those%20of%20the%20Chinese.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20FIR%20has%20its%20roots%20in%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F05%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fneville-roy-singham-china-propaganda.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20August%2C%20which%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-mp-nishikant-dubey-rahul-gandhi-newsclick-independent-journalists-chinese-links-nyt-report%5C%22%3EBJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0cited%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20claim%20that%20Congress%20leaders%20and%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0had%20received%20funds%20from%20China%20to%20create%20an%20%E2%80%9Canti-India%E2%80%9D%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20the%20raids%2C%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20that%20its%20offices%20had%20been%20searched%20and%20the%20devices%20of%20its%20employees%20seized%20by%20government%20agencies%20including%20the%20income%20tax%20department%20since%202021%2C%20but%20the%20government%20had%20been%20unable%20to%20build%20a%20case%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20full%20statement%20from%20December%2019%20is%20reproduced%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20the%20evening%20of%20December%2018%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20been%20unable%20to%20make%20any%20bank%20payments%20due%20to%20action%20by%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20action%2C%20which%20has%20virtually%20frozen%20our%20accounts%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20continuation%20of%20the%20administrative-legal%20siege%20of%20the%20news%20portal%20which%20began%20with%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20raids%20in%20February%202021%2C%20followed%20by%20an%20IT%20department%20survey%20in%20September%202021%2C%20and%20the%20October%203%2C%202023%20crackdown%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20Special%20Cell.%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0founder%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20administrative%20officer%20Amit%20Chakraborty%2C%20arrested%20on%20that%20day%2C%20continue%20to%20languish%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20always%20complied%20with%20the%20laws%20of%20the%20land%2C%20including%20all%20tax%20regulations.%20The%20claims%20levelled%20by%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20are%20without%20any%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0did%20not%20receive%20any%20intimation%20of%20the%20freezing%20of%20accounts%2C%20and%20the%20staff%20discovered%20it%20by%20chance%20while%20trying%20to%20make%20routine%20payments%20last%20evening.%20As%20a%20result%20of%20this%20high-handed%20action%2C%20salaries%20of%20all%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20journalists%2C%20videographers%2C%20and%20administrative%20and%20support%20staff%20%E2%80%94%20and%20consultants%20and%20contributors%20cannot%20be%20paid%2C%20including%20for%20the%2019%20days%20of%20December%20they%20have%20already%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20at%20the%20year-end%20festive%20season%2C%20this%20sudden%20action%20has%20left%20all%20our%20employees%20shocked.%20Since%20there%20is%20no%20indication%20of%20when%20our%20accounts%20will%20become%20accessible%2C%20there%20is%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20all%20employees%20and%20their%20families%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20are%20completely%20dependent%20on%20salaries%20from%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENewsClick.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%20its%20legal%20counsel%20are%20reviewing%20the%20developments.%20Subsequently%2C%20legal%20appeals%20against%20this%20unjust%20and%20cruel%20measure%20will%20be%20initiated%20at%20the%20earliest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%20its%20courageous%20journalists%20remain%20committed%20to%20continuing%20their%20work%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible.%20As%20always%2C%20we%20appeal%20for%20continued%20solidarity%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20source%20of%20support%20and%20encouragement%20to%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703004562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F04143738%2FUntitled-design-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclick-it-department-accounts-frozen%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Denying%20any%20wrongdoing%2C%20the%20online%20news%20portal%20said%20that%20the%20move%20will%20make%20it%20unable%20to%20pay%20its%20employees%20and%20contributors%20for%20work%20they%20have%20so%20far%20done%20in%20December.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclick-it-department-accounts-frozen%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Accenture%20GenAI%20offering%20sees%20momentum%20in%20Q1%20FY24%2C%20signs%20%24450%20mn%20bookings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703003141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fassets%2Fweb-assets%2Fimages%2FBusiness_Standard_685x385.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Faccenture-genai-offering-sees-momentum-in-q1-fy24-signs-450-mn-bookings-123121901328_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20growth%20trajectory%20in%20Q1%20for%20GenAI%20is%20of%20significance%20for%20the%20top%20IT%20services%20players%20who%20are%20eyeing%20this%20segment%20as%20the%20next%20growth%20area%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.