l%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fresolution-professional-calls-for-eoi-for-troubled-gvk-gautami-power-123121901271_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fresolution-professional-calls-for-eoi-for-troubled-gvk-gautami-power-123121901271_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fresolution-professional-calls-for-eoi-for-troubled-gvk-gautami-power-123121901271_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Health%20Ministry%20Writes%20to%20States%20Over%20New%20COVID-19%20Variant%2C%20Asks%20to%20Amp%20up%20Surveillance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19131634%2FScreenshot-2023-12-19-at-1.16.08-PM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20response%20to%20the%20recent%20surge%20in%20COVID-19%20cases%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20detection%20of%20the%20first%20case%20of%20the%20new%20JN.1%20variant%20of%20the%20virus%2C%20the%20Union%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1987840%5C%22%3Ehealth%20ministry%20has%20issued%20a%20directive%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20all%20states%20and%20union%20territories%20(UTs)%20to%20monitor%20the%20situation%20closely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1987840%5C%22%3Eletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20addressed%20to%20them%2C%20the%20ministry%20has%20asked%20states%20to%20monitor%20cases%20of%20influenza-like%20illnesses%20(ILI)%2C%20conduct%20adequate%20testing%2C%20and%20send%20all%20positive%20samples%20for%20whole%20genome%20sequencing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20said%20that%20as%20the%20COVID-19%20virus%20continues%20to%20circulate%20and%20its%20behaviour%20adapts%20to%20Indian%20weather%20conditions%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20to%20uphold%20the%20momentum%20in%20addressing%20public%20health%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20came%20after%20at%20least%20one%20case%20of%20the%20new%20variant%20JN.1%20was%20detected%20during%20routine%20surveillance%20in%20Kerala.%20The%20variant%20was%20also%20detected%20in%20the%20sample%20of%20a%20traveller%20from%20Singapore%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20Tiruchirapalli%2C%20according%20to%20the%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20we%20know%20about%20the%20new%20variant%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sub-variant%20JN.1%20is%20a%20descendant%20of%20the%20BA.2.86%20variant%2C%20commonly%20referred%20to%20as%20Pirola%2C%20and%20is%20not%20exactly%20new.%20The%20first%20cases%20of%20this%20variant%20were%20detected%20in%20the%20United%20States%20in%20September%20and%20the%20first%20case%20globally%20was%20detected%20as%20early%20as%20January%20this%20year%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-health%2Fcentre-writes-to-states-over-new-covid-variant-all-you-should-know-about-jn-1-9073584%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvidence%2C%20so%20far%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20suggest%20that%20JN.1%20can%20cause%20worse%20symptoms%20or%20spread%20faster%20than%20the%20variants%20already%20in%20circulation.%20There%20were%20concerns%20that%20the%20high%20number%20of%20mutations%20could%20mean%20that%20Pirola%20would%20evade%20immune%20response%20more%20easily%20and%20spread%20rapidly%20but%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-health%2Fcentre-writes-to-states-over-new-covid-variant-all-you-should-know-about-jn-1-9073584%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20an%20assessment%20by%20the%20WHO%20Technical%20Advisory%20Group%20on%20COVID-19%20Vaccine%20Composition%20showed%20that%20Pirola%20and%20JN.1%20were%20both%20effectively%20neutralised%20by%20serum%20from%20humans%20who%20had%20had%20the%20infection%20and%20vaccination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrategies%20outlined%20by%20the%20ministry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20health%20secretary%20outlined%20key%20strategies%20for%20COVID%20control%20and%20management%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStates%20have%20been%20advised%20to%20implement%20necessary%20public%20health%20measures%20to%20minimise%20the%20risk%20of%20increased%20disease%20transmission%20ahead%20of%20the%20upcoming%20festive%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20complying%20with%20the%20revised%20surveillance%20strategy%20for%20COVID-19%20provided%20by%20the%20Union%20health%20ministry%2C%20states%20have%20been%20asked%20monitor%20and%20report%20Influenza-like%20Illness%20(ILI)%20and%20severe%20acute%20respiratory%20illness%20(SARI)%20cases%20on%20a%20district-wise%20basis%20and%20regularly%20update%20the%20Integrated%20Health%20Information%20Platform%20(IHIP)%20portal%20to%20detect%20early%20rising%20trends%20in%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20also%20asked%20the%20states%20to%20promote%20community%20awareness%20and%20emphasise%20adherence%20to%20respiratory%20hygiene%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702998975000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19131634%2FScreenshot-2023-12-19-at-1.16.08-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Funion-health-ministry-writes-to-states-over-new-covid-19-variant-asks-to-amp-up-surveillance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Evidence%2C%20so%20far%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20suggest%20that%20JN.1%20can%20cause%20worse%20symptoms%20or%20spread%20faster%20than%20the%20variants%20already%20in%20circulation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F