C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%20(organisation)%2C%20said%20that%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20meeting%20was%20seat-sharing%20and%20all%20leaders%20agreed%20that%20it%20needed%20to%20be%20finalised%20%E2%80%9Cas%20early%20as%20possible%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESome%20sources%20also%20indicated%20that%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20was%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20Congress%20should%20target%20280-300%20seats%20where%20it%20would%20face%20a%20direct%20contest%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20leave%20the%20rest%20for%20other%20constituents.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20have%20a%20one-on-one%20fight%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20insistence%20on%20contesting%20from%20the%20political%20turfs%20of%20its%20allies%20had%20initially%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20roadblock%20for%20seat-sharing%20talks.%20However%2C%20after%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20poor%20performance%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-morning-after-15-takeaways-from-the-four-state-election-results%5C%22%3Ethe%20recent%20assembly%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20may%20budge%20from%20its%20hardened%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EINDIA%20leaders%20also%20decided%20to%20hold%20mass%20protests%20across%20the%20country%20on%20December%2022%20against%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flok-sabha-49-more-opposition-suspended-security-breach-protests%5C%22%3Esuspension%20of%20141%20MPs%20from%20parliament%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EManoj%20Jha%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20said%20that%20all%20leaders%20agreed%20to%20formulate%20a%20mass%20contact%20programme%20and%20a%20plan%20for%20joint%20rallies%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20election%20strategy%20for%20INDIA%20will%20be%20to%20unite%20the%20%E2%80%98PDA%E2%80%99%20(%3Cem%3EPichhda%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20OBC%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20Adivasis)%20group%20to%20challenge%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20also%20means%20that%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20will%20figure%20among%20the%20top-most%20priorities%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20some%20reports%2C%20Banerjee%20proposed%20the%20idea%20of%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20%E2%80%93%20also%20a%20Dalit%20face%20%E2%80%93%20to%20be%20announced%20as%20the%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate.%20The%20proposal%20was%20also%20seconded%20by%20the%20usually%20reticent%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20Kharge%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20name%20of%20the%20leader%20can%20be%20decided%20only%20after%20the%20elections%20and%20added%20that%20the%20primary%20focus%20of%20the%20alliance%20will%20be%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20and%20win%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20unitedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EContrary%20to%20reports%20in%20circulation%20that%20a%20convenor%20would%20be%20announced%20in%20the%20meeting%2C%20some%20MPs%20like%20Manoj%20Jha%20said%20there%20was%20no%20such%20discussion.%20Many%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20including%20the%20convenor%E2%80%99s%20position%2C%20will%20be%20decided%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20idea%20is%20to%20begin%20a%20joint%20campaign%20from%20January%2030%2C%202024%20onwards%20so%20that%20all%20INDIA%20parties%20will%20target%20arriving%20at%20a%20consensus%20on%20the%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20political%20aspects%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20priority%20is%20to%20get%20a%20majority%20by%20contesting%20unitedly%20before%20a%20prime%20ministerial%20face%20could%20be%20decided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20parties%20have%20come%20together%20with%20an%20understanding%20that%20we%20will%20have%20to%20fight%20together%20to%20save%20democracy%20in%20India.%20All%20of%20us%20are%20ready%20for%20the%20fight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20said%2C%20implying%20that%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20is%20not%20just%20yet%20another%20electoral%20contest%2C%20but%20is%20important%20for%20ideological%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20not%20attending%20a%20single%20session%20in%20the%20winter%20session%20of%20parliament%20as%20well%20as%20for%20facilitating%20the%20suspension%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2F141-here-are-all-the-mps-suspended-from-parliament-this-winter-session%5C%22%3Erecord%20number%20of%20MPs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EKharge%20also%20said%20that%20all%20parties%20will%20iron%20out%20their%20differences%20soon%20in%20states%20like%20Bihar%2C%20UP%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Punjab%2C%20where%20different%20INDIA%20constituents%20like%20the%20SP%2C%20AAP%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Thackeray)%20or%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20could%20have%20differences%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20a%20prime%20ministerial%20face%2C%20he%20said%20there%20was%20no%20point%20in%20discussing%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20have%20a%20majority.%20If%20we%20do%20not%20have%20enough%20MPs%2C%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20discussing%20%5Bthe%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20PM%20candidate%5D%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20parties%20also%20passed%20a%20resolution%20on%20EVMs%2C%20saying%20there%20are%20%E2%80%9Cmany%20doubts%20on%20the%20integrity%20of%20their%2