%20we%20see%20a%20clear%20decline.%20The%20ratio%20is%2093%25%20(January-March)%3B%2091%25%20for%20July-September%20and%2089%25%20for%20October-December.%20Thus%2C%20while%20PLFS%20is%20doing%20a%20better%20job%20of%20counting%20economic%20participation%20of%20women%2C%20it%20also%20reveals%20clear%20gaps%20in%20earnings%20of%20the%20self-employed%2C%20the%20category%20of%20women%20that%20is%20driving%20the%20increase%20in%20LFPR%20measurement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20salaried%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20proportion%20of%20women%20in%20regular%20salaried%20work%20has%20not%20increased%2C%20we%20should%20note%20that%20daily%20wages%20for%20rural%20women%20have%20increased%20in%20real%20terms%20(Figure%207)%2C%20as%20indeed%20they%20have%20for%20urban%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19173755%2Fimage-1640.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19173755%2Fimage-1640.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19173755%2Fimage-1640-300x189.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19173755%2Fimage-1640-1024x644.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689873%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22755%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fviz.ceda.ashoka.edu.in%2Fdata-narrative%2F15122023%2Ffigure7a.html%5C%22%3EFigure%207a%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22ht