20in%20the%20labour%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20lessons%20does%20this%20hold%20for%20policy%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20urgent%20need%20to%20increase%20women%E2%80%99s%20participation%20in%20regular%20salaried%20paid%20work%20with%20job%20contracts%20and%20social%20security%20benefits.%20This%20would%20be%20the%20most%20important%20step%2C%20albeit%20not%20the%20only%20one%2C%20towards%20women%E2%80%99s%20economic%20empowerment.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20rural%20non-farm%20paid%20employment%20opportunities%20would%20need%20to%20be%20expanded.%20Additionally%2C%20barriers%20such%20as%20the%20lack%20of%20decent%2C%20fast%20and%20safe%20transportation%20or%20childcare%20facilities%20would%20need%20to%20be%20alleviated%20so%20that%20women%20are%20able%20to%20access%20work%20within%20commuting%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20job%20availability%20and%20the%20demand%20for%20female%20labour%20improves%2C%20women%20will%20gradually%20start%20to%20enter%20paid%20work%2C%20as%20they%20have%20done%20in%20every%20society%20in%20the%20world.%20This%20will%20finally%20start%20to%20shift%20the%20needle%20on%20the%20norm%20that%20prevents%20women%20from%20accessing%20paid%20work%3A%20that%20women%20are%20predominantly%20responsible%20for%20all%20household%20chores%20(cooking%2C%20gathering%20fuel%2C%20cleaning%2C%20washing%20dishes%2C%20laundry%2C%20house%20maintenance%2C%20childcare%2C%20elderly%20care%20etc.).%20History%20tells%20us%20that%20norms%20are%20sticky.%20To%20accelerate%20the%20change%2C%20public%20messaging%20from%20the%20highest%20quarters%20should%20strongly%20advocate%20the%20message%20of%20gender%20equality%20within%20the%20household.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ashoka.edu.in%2Fprofile%2Fashwini-deshpande%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAshwini%20Deshpande%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20professor%20of%20Economics%20at%20Ashoka%20Uni