A0BCCI%C2%A0is%20not%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20a%20complete%20travesty.%20So%20much%20cricketing%20talent%20is%20shut%20out%20because%20the%20game%20is%20run%20by%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20cricket%20fans%2C%20it%20has%20been%20frustrating%20to%20see%20players%20like%20Mithali%20Raj%2C%20Jhulan%20Goswami%20and%2C%20more%20recently%2C%20the%20precocious%20young%20cricketers%20like%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur%2C%20Smriti%20Mandhana%2C%20Shefali%20Verma%2C%20Deepti%20Sharma%20and%20Jemima%20Rodrigues%20sit%20out%20for%20months%20despite%20being%20hungry%20to%20play%2C%20despite%20being%20in%20the%20prime%20of%20their%20lives%2C%20despite%20being%20at%20the%20top%20of%20their%20form%20and%20skill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20even%20more%20inexcusable%20because%20today%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwomens-cricket-is-rife-with-stories-of-sexual-harassment-what-is-the-bcci-doing%5C%22%3EBoard%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20one%20of%20the%20richest%20sports%20bodies%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20money%2C%20the%20resources%2C%20the%20stadiums%2C%20the%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20talent%2C%20the%20fans%2C%20the%20sponsor%20interest%2C%20the%20appetite%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20it%20is%20there%2C%20but%20the%20men%20in%20charge%20have%20been%20dragging%20their%20feet.%20For%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECounter-arguments%20will%20be%20trotted%20out.%20For%20instance%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98Test%20cricket%20is%20dying%2C%20so%20we%20have%20focused%20on%20ODI%20and%20T20%20international%20(T20I)%20cricket%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20women%E2%80%99.%20Or%2C%20%E2%80%98it%20is%20also%20tougher%20to%20market%20women%E2%80%99s%20Test%20matches%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-c