-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19153745%2FCOP_EXPO-CITY-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20sun%20set%20on%20COP28%2C%20a%20gathering%20that%20drew%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20attention%20to%20climate%20change%20and%20its%20multifaceted%20challenges%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20immersed%20in%20a%20sea%20of%20thoughts%2C%20influenced%20by%20my%20journey%20and%20the%20broader%20implications%20of%20our%20collective%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20come%20from%20the%20Pahari%20tribe%20of%20the%20lower%20Himalayan%20region%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20a%20community%20intimately%20connected%20with%20the%20natural%20world%2C%20now%20facing%20the%20brunt%20of%20climate%20change.%20The%20nomadic%20Bakarwal%20community%2C%20our%20neighbours%2C%20epitomises%20this%20struggle.%20Their%20culture%20and%20lifestyle%2C%20intricately%20tied%20to%20traditional%20grazing%20routes%20and%20biodiversity%2C%20are%20under%20siege.%20Climate-induced%20flash%20floods%2C%20land%20degradation%2C%20and%20the%20transformation%20of%20ancient%20nomadic%20paths%20into%20military%20roads%20symbolise%20a%20broader%20issue%20of%20environmental%20injustice%2C%20deeply%20resonant%20with%20loss%20and%20damage%20%E2%80%93%20a%20central%20theme%20at%20COP28.%20The%20river%20Suran%2C%20in%20my%20hometown%20of%20Surankote%20on%20the%20border%20of%20India-Pakistan%2C%20exemplifies%20this%20%E2%80%93%20once%20brimming%20with%20life%2C%20it%20is%20now%20drying%20up%20at%20an%20alarming%20pace%2C%20while%20flash%20floods%20in%20recent%20years%20have%20wreaked%20havoc%20on%20the%20indigenous%20communities%20residing%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fembed%3Fpb%3D!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d13286.686384016855!2d74.24359876703879!3d33.63975613676126!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x38e1d2f6418cd433%253A0x949a627ff9c58acf!2sSurankot!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1702980048328!5m2!1sen!2sin%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20year%E2%80%99s%20conference%20pledged%20a%20modest%20%24700%20million%20to%20the%20loss%20and%20damage%20fund%2C%20a%20figure%20starkly%20inadequate%20when%20considering%20the%20enormity%20of%20the%20need.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20stark%20reminder%20of%20the%20gap%20between%20commitment%20and%20necessity%2C%20especially%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20meagre%20contributions%20from%20industrial%20giants%20like%20the%20USA.%20It%20speaks%20volumes%20of%20the%20chasm%20between%20what%20is%20needed%20and%20what%20is%20offered.%20These%20funds%20should%20prioritise%20projects%20that%20not%20only%20mitigate%20climate%20change%20but%20also%20preserve%20the%20cultural%20heritage%20and%20traditional%20practices%20of%20indigenous%20communities.%20By%20doing%20so%2C%20we%20can%20ensure%20that%20climate%20finance%20serves%20not%20just%20as%20a%20band-aid%20solution%20but%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20sustainable%20and%20inclusive%20development.%20The%20Global%20Stocktake%20report%20launched%20at%20COP28%20is%20a%20comprehensive%20assessment%20of%20progress%20and%20challenges%2C%20that%20underscored%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20a%20global%20shift%20towards%20sustainable%20energy%20sources.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20sobering%20reminder%20of%20our%20collective%20failure%20to%20stay%20on%20track%20with%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20goals.%20It%20also%20lights%20a%20path%20forward%2C%20towards%20a%20greener%2C%20more%20sustainable%20future.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcop28-licypriya-kangujam-global-stocktake%5C%22%3ELatest%20Draft%20of%20Global%20Stocktake%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Inspire%20Hope%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20COP28%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20platform%20for%20highlighting%20deficits.%20I%20was%20part%20of%20the%20delegation%20from%20Julie%E2%80%99s%20Bicycle%2C%20a%20pioneering%20UK-based%20cultural%20organisation%20that%20serves%20as%20a%20torchbearer%20for%20global%20cultural%20advocacy%20in%20climate%20space.%20With%20their%20global%20call%20for%20%E2%80%98Culture%20at%20the%20Heart%20of%20Climate%20Action%E2%80%99%2C%20I%20witnessed%20a%20significant%20stride%20in%20integrating%20culture%20into%20climate%20discourse.%20The%20formation%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Group%20of%20Friends%20for%20Culture-based%20Climate%20Action%E2%80%99%2C%20co-chaired%20by%20the%20UAE%20and%20Brazil%2C%20marked%20a%20pivotal%20shift.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20initiative%2C%20set%20to%20culminate%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98Joint%20Work%20Decision%20on%20Culture%20and%20Climate%20Action%E2%80%99%20at%20COP29%2C%20aims%20to%20infuse%20cultural%20perspectives%20into%20climate%20policies%20at%20COP30%20in%20the%20Amazonian%20heartlands%20of%20Brazil.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20move%20that%20will%20recognise%20the%20cultural%20dimensions%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20promising%20to%20shape%20future%20dialogues%20and%20policies.%20It%20is%20imperative%20to%20build%20on%20this%20momentum%20by%20encouraging%20nations%20to%20develop%20policies%20that%20are%20culturally%20sensitive%20and%20grounded%20in%20the%20realities%20of%20their%20indigenous%20and%20local%20communities.%20This%20can%20be%20achieved%20through%20participatory%20policy-making%20processes%20that%20include%20voices%20from%20all%20sections%20of%20society%2C%20especially%20those%20most%20affected%20by%20climate%20change.%20Culture%2C%20with%20its%20innate%20ability%20to%20evoke%20emotions%20and%20mobilise%20people%2C%20holds%20a%20power%20that%20has%20historically%20been%20perceived%20as%20a%20threat%20by%20authoritarian%20regimes.%20This%20power%20of%20culture%20to%20stir%20emotions%20makes%20it%20an%20impactful%20tool%20for%20climate%20advocacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECOP28%20also%20provided%20a%20stage%20for%20powerful%20expressions%20of%20%E2%80%98artivism%E2%80%99.%20Meeting%20renowned%20Brazilian%20graffiti%20artist%20Mundano%20and%20witnessing%20music%20performances%20by%20indigenous%20women%20at%20the%20Brazil%20pavilion%2C%20I%20was%20reminded%20of%20the%20potent%20role%20art%20plays%20in%20mobilising%20climate%20action%20and%20empathy.%20In%20distributing%20letters%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98Letters%20To%20The%20Earth%E2%80%99%20campaign%2C%20I%20crossed%20paths%20with%20inspiring%20figures%20like%20Ayisha%20Sidiqa%2C%20a%20young%20Pakistani-American%20climate%20activist.%20Her%20impassioned%20speech%20on%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20struck%20a%20deep%20chord%20at%20the%20summit%2C%20echoing%20our%20shared%20struggles%20and%20resilience.%20The%20premiere%20of%20%E2%80%98Act%20Now%20Film%E2%80%99%20was%20another%20emotional%20moment.%20This%20project%2C%20which%20I%20co-directed%20in%20its%20inaugural%20year%20at%20COP26%20in%20Glasgow%2C%20beautifully%20juxtaposes%20grief%20and%20hope%2C%20fear%20and%20optimism%2C%20encapsulating%20the%20emotional%20spectrum%20of%20climate%20advocacy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECOP28%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20without%20its%20challenges.%20As%20a%20youth%20from%20the%20global%20south%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20witnessed%20first-hand%20the%20difficulty%20of%20carving%20out%20a%20space%20in%20climate%20leadership.%20This%20year%E2%80%99s%20COP%2C%20however%2C%20illustrated%20a%20growing%20recognition%20of%20these%20voices%2C%20marking%20a%20positive%20shift%20towards%20inclusivity.%20Samoan%20activist%20Briana%20Freuns%2C%20speaking%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98Why%20the%20World%20Needs%20a%20Fossil%20Fuel%20Non-Proliferation%20Treaty%E2%80%99%20panel%2C%20highlighted%20the%20Pacific%20Island%20nations%E2%80%99%20fight%20for%20the%201.5%C2%B0%20Celsius%20goal%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20that%20our%20communities%20in%20the%20small%20island%20states%20will%20not%20survive%20if%20the%201.5%C2%B0%20C%20goal%20is%20not%20achieved.%E2%80%9D%20Small%20island%20states%2C%20often%20on%20the%20front%20lines%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20continued%20their%20fight%20to%20keep%20the%201.5%C2%B0%20C%20goal%20alive.%20The%20signing%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Fossil%20Fuel%20Non-Proliferation%20Treaty%E2%80%99%20by%20nations%20like%20Palau%2C%20Colombia%2C%20Samoa%2C%20and%20Nauru%20was%20a%20testament%20to%20their%20resilience%20and%20commitment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHosting%20COP28%2C%20the%20UAE%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98petrostate%E2%80%99%2C%20achieved%20a%20historic%20milestone%20by%20uniting%20nearly%20every%20nation%20in%20the%20world%20in%20an%20agreement%20to%20transition%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20even%20with%202%2C456%20fossil%20fuel%20lobbyists%20present%20at%20the%20conference.%20This%20consensus%20reached%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2028%20years%20of%20international%20climate%20negotiations%2C%20marked%20a%20significant%20moment%20in%20our%20collective%20response%20to%20the%20climate%20crisis.%20The%20summit%E2%80%99s%20success%20was%20further%20amplified%20by%20the%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20exemplary%20arrangements%20in%20terms%20of%20safety%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20positioning%20COP28%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20conferences%20since%20COP21%20in%20Paris.%20This%20achievement%20mirrors%20the%20successful%20hosting%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20by%20Qatar%20last%20year%2C%20defying%20scepticism%20and%20mistrust.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20reflection%20of%20a%20broader%20narrative%2C%20often%20laced%20with%20subtle%20biases%20against%20Muslim-majority%20countries.%20As%20we%20look%20towards%20COP29%20in%20Azerbaijan%2C%20these%20underlying%20sentiments%20of%20scepticism%20and%20distrust%20need%20to%20be%20acknowledged%20and%20addressed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20outcome%20of%20COP28%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20without%20its%20complexities.%20Many%20countries%20expressed%20frustration%20over%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20clear%20directive%20for%20a%20fossil-fuel%20%E2%80%9Cphase-out%E2%80%9D%20within%20this%20decade.%20The%20final%20text%2C%20while%20a%20breakthrough%20in%20some%20respects%2C%20was%20critiqued%20for%20having%20a%20%E2%80%9Clitany%20of%20loopholes%E2%80%9D%20that%20could%20potentially%20allow%20the%20continued%20production%20and%20consumption%20of%20coal%2C%20oil%2C%20and%20gas.%20This%20highlights%20the%20ongoing%20challenges%20in%20international%20climate%20negotiations%20%E2%80%93%20balancing%20ambitious%20goals%20with%20pragmatic%20solutions%2C%20and%20the%20varying%20interests%20and%20capabilities%20of%20participating%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20me%2C%20COP28%20was%20more%20than%20a%20conference%3B%20it%20was%20a%20convergence%20of%20culture%2C%20activism%2C%20and%20policy.%20It%20was%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20diverse%20yet%20unified%20nature%20of%20our%20fight%20against%20climate%20change.%20As%20I%20delve%20deeper%20into%20the%20climate%20policy%20space%2C%20I%20am%20eager%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20process%20of%20decision-making%20and%20negotiations.%20The%20journey%20ahead%20is%20long%20and%20arduous.%20The%20commitments%20made%20at%20COP28%20are%20only%20as%20strong%20as%20their%20implementation%2C%20historic%20as%20they%20may%20be%2C%20are%20just%20the%20beginning.%20Transparency%20in%20reporting%20progress%2C%20adherence%20to%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20goals%2C%20and%20active%20engagement%20with%20civil%20society%20will%20be%20key%20to%20ensuring%20that%20the%20promises%20made%20at%20COP28%20translate%20into%20tangible%20action.%20The%20responsibility%20of%20addressing%20climate%20change%20should%20not%20solely%20lie%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20fossil%20fuel-producing%20nations%20but%20equally%20on%20those%20who%20consume%20these%20resources.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20COP28%20was%20a%20mosaic%20of%20hope%20and%20challenge%2C%20progress%20and%20shortfall%2C%20and%20a%20reminder%20of%20our%20shared%20humanity%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20changing%20climate.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20call%20to%20action%2C%20urging%20us%20to%20weave%20the%20threads%20of%20culture%2C%20policy%2C%20and%20activism%20into%20a%20tapestry%20of%20sustainable%20and%20just%20climate%20solutions.%20It%20should%20be%20viewed%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20a%20new%20era%20of%20climate%20action%20%E2%80%93%20one%20that%20is%20more%20inclusive%2C%20culturally%20aware%2C%20and%20practically%20focused.%20As%20I%20reflect%20on%20my%20journey%2C%20from%20a%20village%20nestled%20in%20the%20Pirpanjal%20mountain%20range%20of%20the%20lower%20Himalayas%20to%20the%20global%20stage%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20filled%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose%20and%20resolve%2C%20ready%20to%20contribute%20to%20this%20ever-evolving%20narrative%20of%20climate%20justice%20and%20hope.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESyed%20Jazib%20Ali%20is%20a%20documentarian%20and%20cultural%20practitioner%2C%20whose%20internationally%20acclaimed%20work%20advocates%20for%20fair%20human%20rights%2C%20societal%20equality%20and%20climate%20justice%20on%20a%20global%20stage.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702981831000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19153745%2FCOP_EXPO-CITY-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcop28-global-south-voices-recognition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20youth%20from%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20I've%20witnessed%20first-hand%20the%20difficulty%20of%20carving%20out%20a%20space%20in%20climate%20leadership.%20This%20year's%20COP%2C%20however%2C%20illustrated%20a%20growing%20recognition%20of%20these%20voices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcop28-global-south-voices-recognition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20killed%20near%20England%20cricket%20team's%20hote