0farms%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Nambie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20school%20has%20increased%20from%2019%20to%2085.%20They%20do%20this%20for%20free%2C%20only%20charging%20a%20nominal%20fee%20to%20pay%20the%20other%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20spare%20time%2C%20the%20couple%20tends%20to%20a%20farm%2C%20cultivating%20lemongrass.%20They%20sell%20lemongrass%20oil%2C%20while%20Nambie%20pursues%20her%20passion%20for%20pickling%20by%20starting%20a%20pickle%20business.%20She%20also%20dreams%20of%20opening%20a%20restaurant%20someday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%20important%20to%20Nambie%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332322%2Fabha-singhaal-khichdi-express-model-cloud-kitchen-entreprenuer-business-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteaching%20or%20cooking%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20been%20connected%20to%20food%20and%20I%20really%20enjoy%20being%20around%20children.%20You%20learn%20something%20new%20in%20both%20teaching%20and%20cooking.%20Every%20day%20is%20a%20new%20day%20in%20the%20kitchen%20as%20well%20as%20the%20classroom.%20I%20love%20it.%20Why%20would%20I%20choose%20between%20the%20two%3F%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Nambie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700662812000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FNambi2-1700662473.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334658%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nambie%20Jessica%20Marak%20from%20Meghalaya%20created%20'Eat%20Your%20Kappa'%20on%20YouTube%20to%20showcase%20Northeastern%20culture%20and%20change%20how%20people%20view%20local%20food.%20She's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20top-eight%20finalists%20on%20MasterChef%20India%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3